===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|fulminatus|fulminātus|lang=la}}, past participle of {{term|fulmino|fulminō|lighten, hurl or strike with lightning|lang=la}}, from {{term|fulmen||lightning which strikes and sets on fire, thunderbolt|lang=la}}, from earlier {{recons|fulgmen|lang=la}}, {{recons|fulgimen|lang=la}}, from {{term|fulgo|fulgō|lang=la}}, {{term|fulgeo|fulgeō|flash, lighten|lang=la}}. More at {{l|en|fulgent}}.

